title: [Gyldemar Forest, Depression]
description: Dead leaves and limbs fill the bottom of the depression.  The leaves create a nice spot to rest, while the limbs discourage careless relaxation in the leaf piles.

Dead leaves and limbs fill the bottom of the depression.  The leaves create a nice spot to rest, while the limbs discourage careless relaxation in the leaf piles.  Small animals can be heard scurrying through the leaves in the black of the night.
